Perfect! Now I need to determine which is the first International medal. Let me check which tournament names indicate international competitions:

- "SEA Games" - South East Asian Games (International)
- "World Junior Championships" - World level (International)

Both are international competitions. The earliest medal by year is in 2017 in Yogyakarta. Let me verify this with a proper query that joins all the tables:

function.arguments:
{"command": "psql -c "
SELECT 
    a.name as athlete_name,
    t.name as tournament_name,
    f.name as format_name,
    m.type as medal_type,
    m.year,
    m.location
FROM athlete a
JOIN tournament t ON a.athlete_id = t.athlete_id
JOIN format f ON t.tournament_id = f.tournament_id
JOIN medal m ON f.format_id = m.format_id
WHERE a.name = 'Pitha Haningtyas Mentari'
ORDER BY m.year ASC, m.medal_id ASC
LIMIT 1;
""}
